heading: Hive Dungeon Guide
content: Hive is fast dungeon that has Spiders, which is one of the best monster families in the game. It has the , which is better saved for endgame. Stock up on your Sigils for this one; you'll run it over and over again for massive hordes of loot! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
